    AdapterPackage.AdapterAPI1toAPI2
    The AdapterPackage.AdapterAPI1toAPI2 class adapts an AdapterPackage.API1 instance to behave as an AdapterPackage.API2 instance, allowing rectangles to be drawn using AdapterPackage.API1 coordinates but accessed via AdapterPackage.API2.
    AdapterPackage.AdapterAPI2toAPI1
    The AdapterPackage.AdapterAPI2toAPI1 class adapts an AdapterPackage.API2 instance to behave as an AdapterPackage.API1 instance, allowing rectangles to be drawn using AdapterPackage.API2 coordinates but accessed via AdapterPackage.API1.
    AdapterPackage.API1
    The AdapterPackage.API1 interface provides a method for drawing a rectangle by specifying its position and dimensions.
    AdapterPackage.API1Class
    The AdapterPackage.API1Class class implements the AdapterPackage.API1 interface and provides a way to draw a rectangle by specifying its position and dimensions.
    AdapterPackage.API2
    The AdapterPackage.API2 interface provides a method for drawing a rectangle by specifying two corner points.
    AdapterPackage.API2Class
    The AdapterPackage.API2Class class implements the AdapterPackage.API2 interface and provides a way to draw a rectangle by specifying two opposite corner points.
    AdapterPackage.Main
    AdapterPackage.Main class that represents a client-side application, demonstrates the use of adapters.
